message: Let's be fair, 60-40 is a good start!
Your turn Alice. I'm feeling generous, but let's be realistic. This is a good deal before inflation hurts us both.
Come on Bob, meet me in the middle, we both get less if we wait!
Alice, we're running out of time! This is my final offer, take it or leave it.
You said that was your final offer, but I'm not buying it. Let's compromise!
